<item>
            <title>[LU-1122] MDS got LBUG after upgrade from 1.8.7-RHEL5 to 2.1.55-RHEL6 and then downgrade to 2.1.0-RHEL6</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1122</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Before upgrade,the system configuration is one MDS(1.8.7-RHEL5), two OSS(1.8.7-RHEL5 and 2.1.0-RHEL6) and two clients(1.8.7-RHEL5 and 1.8.7-RHEL6), then upgrade servers and clients to 2.1.55-RHEL6, check the system, works fine. Then do the downgrade, MDS downgrade to 2.1.0-RHEL6, OSS downgrade to 1.8.7-RHEL5 and 2.1.0-RHEL6, clients downgrade to 2.1.0-RHEL5 and 2.1.0-RHEL6&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Got LBUG when checking the dir/files in the OST pool. MDS console log please see the attached.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
